msgid "The *On Master* effect category provides audio visualization effects and filters that only work as a Master effect. That means they apply to the entire project and thus the final render."
msgstr ""

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../effects_and_filters/video_effects/on_master.rst:21
msgid "The effects can be stacked and do influence each other, so the sequence in the Master effect stack **is** important. The only exception is :doc:`/effects_and_filters/video_effects/on_master/audio_wave` that overlays over everything else."
msgstr ""

